<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.3.1">
<l>oḻivil kālamellā muṭaṉāy maṉṉi</l>
<l>vaḻuvilā vaṭimai ceyya vēṇṭunām</l>
<l>teḻiku ralaru vittiru vēṅkaṭat</l>
<l>teḻilkoḷ cōti yentaitantai tantaikkē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Staying, being together all the time without end,</l>
<l>we will want do faultless service</l>
<l>on sacred Vēṅkaṭam with waterfalls with resounding voices</l>
<l>to the father of the father of our father with beautiful light.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
